Ask HN: Help editing upcoming “Facebook and Pedophiles and Autism” true story?
text:
You read that headline correctly and it's not click-bait - there is an actual true story here that is still unfolding. I'm the one who put the pieces together. I'm the one who alerted people during a time when I'm being accused of maliciousness and abuse. I'm also one of the primary caregivers for the desired target. This means, in my view, legally speaking I will be able to prove harm - know why I'm glad I have a great counselor / therapist / human being to discuss this stuff with? Times like these.

Please respond here or via my Medium page or drop your @ and if I get back into Twitter I'll make contact.

Not in a rush to crank it out - still developing - but definitely figuring it's the perfect Christmas Morning reading for Zuckerberg.
